  "text": "To distinguish the allele pvr2 7 from the others, we analysed the sequence of the eIF4E cDNAs from the F2 'Perennial' (pvr2 cDNA-specific primers (forward primer 59-AAAAGCACACAGC-ACCAACA-39 and reverse primer 59-TATTCCGACATTGCATCAA-GAA-39). Each amplification product was sequenced by GenomeExpress (Grenoble, France). Nucleotide sequences were analysed with Chromas Lite 2.01 software (http://www.Technelysium.com.au). The nucleotide and amino acid sequences were aligned with the eIF4E cDNA sequences [GenBank accession nos AY723737 (pvr2 3 ) and EU106863 (pvr2 7 )] using CLUSTAL W (1.82) [CITATION_1] .",
